表格工资管理的代码预览

if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('SalaryManage')
and type = 'U')
drop table SalaryManage
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: SalaryManage */
/*==============================================================*/
create table SalaryManage (
ID int not null,
EmployeeName varchar(20) not null,
CardID varchar(20) not null,
Do_No varchar(20) not null,
MachineNo varchar(20) not null,
MouldNo varchar(20) not null,
ProductNo varchar(20) not null,
Num int null,
BeginDate datetime null,
EndDate datetime null,
ProductDesc varchar(200) not null,
MachineWage decimal(8,2) null default 0,
TimeWage decimal(8,2) null default 0,
CheckWage decimal(8,2) null default 0,
JobWage decimal(8,2) null default 0,
ServiceWage decimal(8,2) null default 0,
OtherWage decimal(8,2) null default 0,
AdjustWage decimal(8,2) null default 0,
WageFlag int null default 0,
Remark varchar(200) null,
CreateDate datetime null,
EmpID varchar(20) null,
constraint PK_SALARYMANAGE primary key (ID)
)
go

declare @CurrentUser sysname
select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_addextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'机台工资管理',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'SalaryManage'
go
